Class CompressionContext.ValueCompressor

java.lang.Object
org.apache.hadoop.hbase.regionserver.wal.CompressionContext.ValueCompressor
Enclosing class:
CompressionContext
static class CompressionContext.ValueCompressor extends Object
Encapsulates the compression algorithm and its streams that we will use for value compression in this WAL.
